  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Striker. Your attack powers are highly damaging and often weaken or hamper the target in some way. You can elude attacks by flying, teleporting, or turning invisible</p><p><strong>Power Source:</strong>  Arcane. You gain your magical power from a pact you forge with a powerful, supernatural force or an unnamed entity.</p><p><strong>Key Abilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Charisma</p></li><li><p>Constitution</p></li><li><p>Intelligence</p></li></ul><p><strong>Armour Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.GwsMGFG3ogxFrvmJ]{Cloth armor (basic clothing)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.lnYMh2YvKedWTpCt]{Leather armor}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Weapon Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.kjW9S8gIQ0LBMF53]{Simple Melee Weapons}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.G50MDDGV8v1NRT9u]{Simple Ranged Weapons}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Implements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.qbmKTq9NKDp8babL]{Rod}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.BGZ4QKJlyb1ebEXv]{Wand}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Bonus to Defences:</strong></p><ul><li><p>+1 Reflex</p></li><li><p>+1 Will</p></li></ul><p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> [[12]] + Con Score</p><p><strong>Hit Points per Level Gained:</strong> [[5]]</p><p><strong>Base Healing Surges per Day:</strong> [[6]] + Con Mod</p><p><strong>Skill Training:</strong> Choose four from the following list:</p><ul><li><p>Arcana (Int)</p></li><li><p>Bluff (Cha)</p></li><li><p>History (Int)</p></li><li><p>Insight (Wis)</p></li><li><p>Intimidate (Cha)</p></li><li><p>Religion (Int)</p></li><li><p>Streetwise (Cha)</p></li><li><p>Thievery (Dex)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Class Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Eldritch blast</p></li><li><p>Prime Shot</p></li><li><p>Shadow Walk</p></li><li><p>Warlock's Curse</p></li></ul><p><strong>Choose one of the following Eldritch Pacts:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Fey Pact</p></li><li><p>Infernal Pact</p></li><li><p>Star Pact</p></li></ul>",
